<h2 class="bold font-l">Sally Bollywood [Vampire Prank]</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Scene from Sally Bollywood, Fangs A Lot. One of the kids scare the local bully, Bob, by suddenly flashing fangs at him. Bob hires the SBI to look into the matter if the kid really is a vampire. Eventually Sally hits upon a break in the case...by revealing that she's been turned into a vampire herself! </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MassiveMultiplayerScam" class='trope-example-link'>Massive Multiplayer Scam</a></p>
